{"tid":191553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊凡卡：以子女在習近平前獻唱《茉莉花》為傲","createTime":"2017-04-08T03:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T10:13:05.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37057682c122ad81821e3a465d8b3d3ead207346","tid":191553,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"「習川會」結束，川普的女兒伊凡卡推文表示，對自己的女兒阿拉貝拉和兒子約瑟夫，為習近平主席和其夫人彭麗媛表演，歡迎他們到美國進行正式訪問，感到非常驕傲。川普總統隨後重推了伊凡卡的推文。<br />\n<br />\n習近平和彭麗媛伉儷拜訪「海湖」俱樂部時，川普女兒伊凡卡和庫許納夫婦在場作陪。伊凡卡並特地讓會說中文的女兒阿拉貝拉和兒子約瑟夫演唱《茉莉花》，背誦《三字經》和唐詩。川普當時也在場聆賞一對孫子女表演。<br />\n---<br />\n川普女兒全面奶共"},{"pid":"6297937391acf685de9d1486473ccbc7d57ca309","tid":191553,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/08/114900_51c365cf1fe5efc24fbefec2e01f8e5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F08%2F114900_51c365cf1fe5efc24fbefec2e01f8e5d.jpg&h=a8c394f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n養兵千日，用在一時"},{"pid":"cbeddc75fb528cb57b1d16c4a2d175b05e7a5943","tid":191553,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"蝗語唐詩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab05096283729c96830c044551d10ffe3cfd554","tid":191553,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:53:16.000Z","msg":"唱首歌又可以打飛機<br />\n支那積弱唔係冇原因"},{"pid":"ddde36078f81428eeb109493cac34c9746bd1c01","tid":191553,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"張圖影側面<br />\n見到兩個元首都好肥 兩隻肥豬<br />\n笑死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a9777286d5bad30903ef6e2e2ffcde826ffc8d","tid":191553,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"習近平個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 